Peace Ewomazino Efih (amụrụ n'ụbọchị nke 5 n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ n'afọ 2000) bụ onye Naijirịa na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agba dịka onye na-agba ọsọ n'etiti maka klọb Ligat Nashim nke Israel FC Kiryat Gat na ndị otu ụmụ nwanyị Naijiria. Ọ gbara bọọlụ maka Edo Queens na Rivers Angels na Nigeria Women Premier League
Na 2018 WAFU Zone B Women's Cup, Efih gbara naanị goolu n'egwuregwu mbụ nke Naịjirịa na asọmpi ahụ.
Na Julaị 2019, Efih bịanyere aka na Sporting de Huelva na nkwekọrịta otu afọ.
